Package org.mitre.provenance.services

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActorServices
    Actor services exposes RESTful services that allow users to interact with actors in the PLUS system.
    DAGServices
    DAGServices encompassess RESTful services that operate over provenance "DAGs" (directed acyclic graphs).
    FeedEntryFactory
    Constructs the specified feed entry
    Feeds
    Services in this class produce RSS/XML and JSON feeds of the latest objects reported to PLUS in various categories.
    FitnessServices
    Services which drive the "fitness widget" functionality.
    NPIDServices
    Services related to non-provenance identifiers.
    ObjectServices
    Object services encompass RESTful services for access to individual provenance objects.
    PrivilegeServices
    Privilege services exposes RESTful services that allow users to interact with privilege sets in the PLUS system.
    ServiceUtility
    This class provides utility methods as helpers for other service implementations.
    WorkflowServices
    Workflow services encompass RESTful services which provide access to workflows and their members.
